# Random Number Generation
### Coin Flips
\centering
\textbf{What is the probability that any independent coin flip will land on heads?} \pause \par \vspace{5mm}
\textbf{Does this change if I flip 50 times?} \pause \par \vspace{5mm}
\textbf{Does this change if I flip 100 times?} \pause \par \vspace{5mm}
\textbf{What about 1000 times?}\pause \par \vspace{5mm}
\textbf{What about 10000 times?}

### Coin Flips (Cont.) {.fragile}
\small
```{r coin_flips_sim, echo=FALSE, tidy = TRUE}
options(width = 55)
set.seed(1234) # Set Random Seed
coin_50 <- data.frame(side = sample(c('heads', 'tails'), size = 10, replace = TRUE)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = side)) + 
  geom_bar()
coin_100 <- data.frame(side = sample(c('heads', 'tails'), size = 10, replace = TRUE))
coin_1000 <- data.frame(side = sample(c('heads', 'tails'), size = 10, replace = TRUE))
coin_10000 <- data.frame(side = sample(c('heads', 'tails'), size = 10, replace = TRUE))




```
